  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个简单的状态流转图，展示用户从首页可以跳转到哪两个页面。核心状态就三个：首页、详情页，还有设置页。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Home",
        "Detail",
        "Settings"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。所以Home是中心节点，Detail和Settings都是它可以直接到达的状态？还是这三个状态之间也有互相跳转的关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Home",
        "Detail",
        "Settings"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "目前只考虑从Home出发的单向关系。用户从首页可以进入详情页，也可以进入设置页。但Detail和Settings之间暂时不需要连线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Home",
        "Detail",
        "Settings"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，那就是Home分别连接Detail和Settings，形成一个简单的星形结构。我用stateDiagram-v2来画，这样语义更清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Home",
        "Detail",
        "Settings",
        "stateDiagram-v2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "对，v2版本的状态图语法更规范。另外确认一下，连线用双横线表示无方向的状态转换关系，这个符合我们的需求，因为只是表示可以到达，不强调严格的流程方向。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Home",
        "Detail",
        "Settings",
        "--"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已经画好了。Home在上方，Detail和Settings分别位于左下和右下，两条连线从Home延伸出去。你看看这个布局可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Home",
        "Detail",
        "Settings"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "整体没问题，但我注意到Settings的标签大小写需要统一。我们产品里一直用的是首字母大写的Settings，不是全小写的settings。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Settings"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，已经修正为Settings。现在三个状态的命名都统一为首字母大写格式了。最终结构是Home同时连接Detail和Settings，没有其他交叉关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Home",
        "Detail",
        "Settings"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
